Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 4.4 05/23] dmaengine: rcar-dmac: Reject zero-length slave DMA requests
Date:   Fri, 26 Jul 2019 09:45:04 -0400
Message-Id: <20190726134522.13308-5-sashal@kernel.org>
